## 🌟 Using String.duplicate

To repeat something many times:

```elixir
# Repeat asterisks
IO.puts(String.duplicate("*", 10))

# Repeat emojis
IO.puts(String.duplicate("⭐", 5))

# Create lines
IO.puts(String.duplicate("-", 20))
```

## 🎨 Patterns

```elixir
# Star pattern
IO.puts(String.duplicate("* ", 10))
IO.puts(String.duplicate(" *", 10))
IO.puts(String.duplicate("* ", 10))
IO.puts(String.duplicate(" *", 10))
```

